                <p>To the extent of any inconsistency between the terms of this Addendum, the Service Agreement, the provisions of this Addendum shall prevail. </p>
                <p>Unless otherwise defined herein, capitalized terms used herein shall have the meanings ascribed to them in the Service Agreement</p>
                <p>Save for changes/ additions specified herein this Addendum, all the other terms and conditions of the Service Agreement shall remain unchanged and in full force and effect.</p>
